title: Champion
subTitle: Rajveer, a police officer, is tasked with protecting a nine-year-old heir, Abbas. However, the job gets complicated when Nazir, a dangerous criminal, seeks to harm the child.

title: Hera Pheri
subTitle: Vijay and Ajay make a living by stealing money from people. Their friendship is affected when Vijay discovers that Ajay's father may have been his father's killer.

title: Sauda
subTitle: Jyoti and Deepak fall in love and get married to each other. However, due to several misunderstandings and financial troubles, they get separated.

title: Souten
subTitle: Shyam, a middle-class man, falls in love with a millionaire's daughter and marries her. However, as their relationship starts deteriorating, Shyam finds solace in the company of Radha.

title: Boss
subTitle: Disowned by his father as a boy, Surya seeks protection from a crime boss. When his brother is wrongfully sent to prison, his father begs him to intervene.

title: Ghar Ghar Ki Kahani
subTitle: Ram begins to suspect that his wife, Seeta, is having an affair with his brother, Amar. His suspicion remains even after Amar gets married, creating problems within his family.

title: Daag: The Fire
subTitle: Karan, a former soldier, learns that his father committed suicide after being accused of a crime he did not commit. So he sets out to exact revenge on the lawyer who is responsible for his loss.

title: Vishwatma
subTitle: A policeman and a reformed criminal go to Kenya to comprehend a syndicate leader. However, they must break the rules of the land defended by Surya Pratap, a Kenyan police inspector.

title: Amar Akbar Anthony
subTitle: Three brothers, each raised in different religious households, reunite after many years in a chance encounter. They set out to take revenge on those responsible for separating them.

title: Amar Akbar Anthony
subTitle: Three brothers, each raised in different religious households, reunite after many years in a chance encounter. They set out to take revenge on those responsible for separating them.

title: Benaam
subTitle: Amit and Sheela, a married couple, save a stabbing victim from an attempted murder. However, things take a dark turn when they start receiving death threats from an unknown person.

title: Rajoo Dada
subTitle: Rajoo intends to exact revenge on his parents' killers and grows up to be a criminal. However, he needs to join hands with his brother, who is a police officer, to find the culprits.

title: Vidhaata
subTitle: After the death of his parent, Kunal lives with his grandfather Shamsher. However, when he falls in love with Durga, Shamsher plans to separate them.

title: Tanhaji: The Unsung Warrior
subTitle: Tanhaji, a Maratha warrior, is Shivaji Maharaj's trusted lieutenant. When the Mughals invade and conquer Kondhana fort, he sets out to reclaim it for his king and country.

title: Ghulam-E-Musthafa
subTitle: A notorious hitman forsakes a life of crime after his lady love suffers a tragic death due to his professional rivalries. However, the mafia compels him to return for a final hit job.

title: Kuch Kuch Hota Hai
subTitle: After reading the letter her mother had written for her before she died, Anjali decides to bring together her widowed father, Rahul, with his true love who is also named Anjali.

title: Ishq
subTitle: Ranjit and Harbanslal, two rich businessmen, hatch a malicious plan when they discover that their children have fallen in love with individuals from the poorer sections of society.

title: Karishma Kali Kaa
subTitle: A devout young woman is falsely accused of murdering a priest and absconding with the temple jewels. With her fate hanging in the balance, the woman seeks divine intervention to prove her innocence.

title: Karishma Kali Kaa
subTitle: A devout young woman is falsely accused of murdering a priest and absconding with the temple jewels. With her fate hanging in the balance, the woman seeks divine intervention to prove her innocence.

title: Kartoos
subTitle: ACP Jay Suryavanshi assigns an inmate on death row, Jeet, the task of killing Jagat, a terrorist. Things take a turn when Jeet falls in love with Mini and gets distracted from his mission.

title: Masoom
subTitle: D K Malhotra leads a peaceful life with his wife and two daughters. But all of this changes when he is forced to bring a boy, who is his son from a previous relationship, home after his mother dies.

title: Bal Hanuman Return Of The Demon
subTitle: Bal Hanuman and his friends join together to defeat the crocodile demon who has been brought to life in order to create havoc on Earth.

title: Hello Brother
subTitle: In a heated confrontation, Hero is shot dead and his heart is transplanted into Inspector Vishal. As a bizarre consequence, Hero's ghost haunts Vishal, demanding revenge for his murder.

title: Dilwale
subTitle: Despite the family rivalry, Raj and Meera fall in love other but a misunderstanding causes them to part ways. Years later, fate brings them together when their siblings fall for each other.

title: Gabbar Is Back
subTitle: The city's administration wrongs Aditya, a commoner. To avenge his tragedy, he disguises himself as a vigilante, Gabbar, and teams up with honest government officers to expose the corrupt.

title: Dil Hai Tumhaara
subTitle: Sarita raises Shalu, her spouse's love child, and her daughter, Nimmi, but she does not forgive Shalu's past. When she discovers that Shalu is growing close to Nimmi's lover, things become worse.

title: Sholay
subTitle: Jai and Veeru, two ex-convicts, are hired by Thakur Baldev Singh, a retired policeman, to help him nab Gabbar Singh, a notorious dacoit, who has spread havoc in the village of Ramgarh.

title: Apmaan Ki Aag
subTitle: While celebrating his girlfriend Mona's birthday, Vikrant gets humiliated by two goons. He vows to exact revenge but it takes him down a difficult and thorny path.
